      "Ok maybe time to wrap this up and go into hibernation for a week before the big Halloween season starts.  Iâ€™ve already talked about the lists, years, labels, categories and ratings, so I think all thatâ€™s left for me to talk about are some individual movies.  Of course, I have to do a top 10 and a bottom 10 with some honorable mentions, then maybe some specific mentions.",
